<paragraph id="IFRS12_BC61A"><paranum>BC61A</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 12"/><data name="paranum" value="BC61A"/></prolog><body><variant base="SL36823314" id="IFRS12_BC61A_V1"> <p id="IFRS12_P0477"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Entities</ph></ph> (Amendments to <xref base="F36823316" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_TOC.dita#IFRS10_TOC0001" id="IFRS12_X0496">IFRS 10</xref>, <xref base="F36823317" href="IFRS12_TOC.dita#IFRS12_TOC0001/IFRS12_TOC0001_V1" id="IFRS12_X0497">IFRS 12</xref> and <xref base="F36823318" href="../ias27/IAS27_TOC0001.dita#IAS27_TOC0001" id="IFRS12_X0498">IAS 27</xref>) introduced a requirement for investment entities to measure their investments in particular subsidiaries at fair value through profit or loss instead of consolidating them. The Board also decided on specific disclosure requirements for investment entities.</p></variant></body></paragraph>